).containsExactly(1, 2);\n        assertThat(bean.getPlainText()).isEqualTo(\"plain\");\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void setPropsAttemptsFallbackInvocationWhenArrayConversionFails() {\n        final SetterBean bean = new SetterBean();\n        final JSONPojoConvertor convertor = new JSONPojoConvertor(SetterBean.class);\n        final Map properties = new LinkedHashMap();\n        properties.put(\"labels\", new Object[] {new Object()});\n        properties.put(\"scores\", new Object[] {Integer.valueOf(1), \"not a number\"});\n\n        final int updatedProperties = convertor.setProps(bean, properties);\n\n        assertThat(updatedProperties).isZero();\n        assertThat(bean.getLabels()).isNull();\n        assertThat(bean.getScores()).isNull();\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void setPropsUsesOriginalNumericArrayWhenElementConversionFails() {\n        final SetterBean bean = new SetterBean();\n        final JSONPojoConvertor convertor = new JSONPojoConvertor(SetterBean.class);\n        final Integer[] originalScores = new Integer[] {Integer.valueOf(1), null, Integer.valueOf(3)};\n        final Map properties = new LinkedHashMap();\n        properties.put(\"boxedScores\", originalScores);\n\n        final int updatedProperties = convertor.setProps(bean, properties);\n\n        assertThat(updatedProperties).isEqualTo(1);\n        assertThat(bean.getBoxedScores()).isSameAs(originalScores);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void setterUsesOriginalArrayWhenNonNumericArrayCopyFails() throws NoSuchMethodException,\n            InvocationTargetException, IllegalAccessException {\n        final SetterBean bean = new SetterBean();\n        final Object[] originalValues = new Object[] {new Object()};\n        final Method method = SetterBean.class.getMethod(\"setFallbackValue\", Object.class);\n        final ObjectAcceptingArraySetter setter = new ObjectAcceptingArraySetter(\"fallbackValue\", method);\n\n        setter.invoke(bean, originalValues);\n\n        assertThat(bean.getFallbackValue())